## ðŸ”„ How Machine Learning Works

1. **Data Input** â†’  
   Raw data (text, images, etc.) is fed into the ML system.

2. **Training** â†’  
   The system processes data through ML algorithms to "learn" patterns.

3. **Testing & Validation** â†’  
   A separate set of data is used to check how well the model performs.

4. **Production Use** â†’  
   Once validated, the trained model is used to make real-world predictions or decisions.

